description.en: GazeCoin is the first immersive advertising platform for monetising VR. GazeCoin creates a business model of VR and AR by creating exchange units among content owners, advertisers, users, first measured in line of sight, more specifically through gaze tracking We use the concept of gaze. Content bidders receive incentives to offer the most interesting content by billing advertisers for a time that users are really interested in. In addition, the model gives the user a reward for consuming the content so that the content can be provided free of charge.
